Title: Darkness Falls
Plot: When a group of loggers in the Washington State National Forest disappear in the same way that another group disappeared 50 years ago, Mulder and Scully go along to investigate and find themselves trapped in a cabin surrounded by flesh eating insects that only attack at night.
GuestStars: Jason Beghe, Tom O'Rourke, Barry Greene, David Hay, Ken Tremblett, Titus Welliver
